 radiation has no effect on the eigenvalues of an electron of\nhelium for a particular electric field intensity directed along $z$-axis. Also,\nfor a very strong external electric field and an infinitesimal screening\nparameter, the system is strongly bound. This work has potential application in\nthe areas of atomic and molecular processes in external fields including\ninteractions with strong fields and short pulses.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Sun, 11 Dec 2016 17:14:39 GMT"}],"update_date":"2017-01-09"}
